    "Applicability of our solutionBased on our perspective model, we demonstrate the applicability of our proposed solution for scheduling Cloud-Edge Continuum workloads when considering appropriate energy sources, energy providers, infrastructures, and controllers (centralized and distributed).We illustrate six different scenarios for delay-sensitive requests through a sequence diagram in Fig. 14.",
    "Here, the objective is to maximize the utilization of renewable energy in the federated Cloud-Edge Continuum.",
